I bought this movie for my husband, because he used to watch it when he was younger. However, my 4 year old son loves it even more! He watches 3 to 4 times in a row and almost everyday. We love it!
I loved this show growing up. When i watch it now its a lil corny, but i do wish there were more than 3 episodes available. I was extremely to see it on amazon.

Product was listed as new but was definitely used.  The entire DVD was covered in scratches.  Luckily the disc still plays.  I would be hesitant about buying this product from the same supplier I did.
